# UACF - Unity Autonomous Control Framework

This project includes UACF, an HTTP API server in Unity Editor for AI agent control.

## UACF API (localhost:7890)

When Unity Editor is running, the UACF server provides these endpoints:

### Status & Health
- `GET /api/ping` - Lightweight health check (no main thread); use when /api/status hangs
- `GET /api/status` - Server status, Unity version, project info, is_compiling, active_scene, uptime

### Assets
- `POST /api/assets/refresh` - Refresh AssetDatabase
- `GET /api/assets/find?filter=t:Script&path=Assets/Scripts` - Find assets
- `POST /api/assets/create-folder` - Body: `{"path":"Assets/Scripts/Player"}`
- `DELETE /api/assets/delete` - Body: `{"path":"Assets/Scripts/Old.cs"}`

### Compilation
- `POST /api/compile/request` - Body: `{"wait":true,"timeout_seconds":60}` - Trigger compile, optionally wait
- `GET /api/compile/status` - Current compilation status
- `GET /api/compile/errors?severity=error` - Get last compile errors/warnings

### Files
- `POST /api/file/write` - Body: `{"path":"Assets/Scripts/X.cs","content":"...","auto_refresh":true,"wait_compile":true}`
- `GET /api/file/read?path=Assets/Scripts/X.cs` - Read file

### Scenes
- `GET /api/scene/list` - List loaded scenes
- `POST /api/scene/open` - Body: `{"path":"Assets/Scenes/X.unity","mode":"Single"}`
- `POST /api/scene/save` - Save active scene
- `POST /api/scene/new` - Body: `{"path":"Assets/Scenes/New.unity","template":"default"}`
- `GET /api/scene/hierarchy?include_components=true&depth=3` - Get hierarchy

### GameObjects
- `POST /api/gameobject/create` - Body: `{"name":"Player","tag":"Player","components":[{"type":"Rigidbody","fields":{"mass":1}}]}`
- `GET /api/gameobject/find?name=Player` - Find by name/tag/path/component
- `PUT /api/gameobject/modify` - Body: `{"target":{"instance_id":123},"set":{"name":"X","active":true}}`
- `DELETE /api/gameobject/destroy` - Body: `{"target":{"name":"Player"}}`
- `POST /api/gameobject/set-parent` - Body: `{"target":{"name":"X"},"parent":{"name":"Y"}}`
- `POST /api/gameobject/duplicate` - Body: `{"target":{"name":"X"},"new_name":"X (2)"}`

### Components
- `POST /api/component/add` - Body: `{"target":{"name":"Player"},"component_type":"Rigidbody","fields":{"mass":1}}`
- `GET /api/component/get?instance_id=123&component=PlayerController` - Get component fields
- `PUT /api/component/set-fields` - Body: `{"target":{"name":"Player"},"component":"PlayerController","fields":{"moveSpeed":7.5}}`
- `DELETE /api/component/remove` - Body: `{"target":{"name":"Player"},"component":"BoxCollider"}`
- `GET /api/component/list-types?filter=Collider` - List available component types

### Prefabs
- `POST /api/prefab/create` - Body: `{"source":{"instance_id":123},"path":"Assets/Prefabs/X.prefab"}`
- `POST /api/prefab/instantiate` - Body: `{"prefab_path":"Assets/Prefabs/X.prefab","name":"X_01"}`
- `PUT /api/prefab/modify` - Body: `{"prefab_path":"...","operations":[{"action":"add_component","component":"AudioSource"}]}`

### Batch
- `POST /api/batch/execute` - Body: `{"operations":[{"id":"op1","endpoint":"POST /api/gameobject/create","body":{...}}],"stop_on_error":true}`

### Editor
- `POST /api/editor/play` - Start Play Mode
- `POST /api/editor/stop` - Stop Play Mode
- `POST /api/editor/pause` - Pause/Resume

### Project
- `GET /api/project/settings?category=tags` - Get tags/layers
- `POST /api/project/add-tag` - Body: `{"tag":"Enemy"}`
- `POST /api/project/set-layer` - Body: `{"layer_index":8,"name":"Player"}`

## Target format
- `{"instance_id": 12345}` - By Instance ID
- `{"name": "Player"}` - By name
- `{"path": "Canvas/Panel"}` - By hierarchy path
- `{"tag": "Player"}` - By tag

## Field value formats
- Primitives: `5.0`, `"hello"`, `true`
- Vector3: `{"x":1,"y":2,"z":3}`
- Reference: `{"reference":{"name":"GroundCheck"}}` or `{"reference":{"instance_id":123}}`
- Asset: `{"asset":"Assets/Materials/Red.mat"}`
